Hello all,

I recently took over FRC 4601, The Circuitbirds, as lead mentor and I am getting back into the swing of things. I am not really sure if this is the right place for this question, but I was looking over things we may need and I was visiting the Rev Robotics website and saw they came up with a new control system for FRC. I was wondering if this was every team had to change over to this? or if it is an optional thing.

Thank you in advance,

Bobby Hudock
Lead Mentor
Team 4601
Canfield Circuitbirds
